<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0754a13shiHongRen"><lb
n="0754a13" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0754a13"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028112">蘄州東山</placeName><persName key="A000237">弘忍</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0754a14"/><persName key="A000237">釋弘忍</persName>，姓周氏，家寓<placeName key="PL000000018847">淮左潯陽</placeName>，一云<placeName key="PL000000028124">黃梅</placeName>人<lb
ed="T" n="0754a15"/>也。王父<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1306"/>暨考，皆干名不利，賁于丘園<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1217"/>。其母<lb
ed="T" n="0754a16"/>始娠，移月而光照庭室，終夕若晝。其生也<lb
ed="T" n="0754a17"/>灼爍如初，異香襲人，舉家欣駭。迨能言，辭<lb
ed="T" n="0754a18"/>氣與隣兒弗類。既成童丱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g635"/>，絕其遊弄。厥父<lb
ed="T" n="0754a19"/>偏愛，因令誦書，無記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1312"/>應阻其宿熏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1090"/>，真心早<lb
ed="T" n="0754a20"/>萌其成現。一旦出<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz2"/>明<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz2"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0754001"/>徙<anchor xml:id="end0754001"/>倚間如有所待，時<lb
ed="T" n="0754a21"/><placeName key="PL000000028112">東山</placeName><persName key="A003654">信<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>邂逅至焉。問<ref type="person" target="#A000237">之</ref>曰：「何姓名乎？」對<lb
ed="T" n="0754a22"/>問朗暢，區別有歸，理逐言分，聲隨響答。<persName key="A003654">信<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0754a23"/>熟視之，歎曰：「此非凡童也！具體<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1307"/>占之，止<lb
ed="T" n="0754a24"/>闕七大人之相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1213"/>，不及<persName key="A002799">佛</persName>矣。苟預法流，二十<lb
ed="T" n="0754a25"/>年後必大作佛事，勝任荷寄。<ptr target="#n1303"/>」乃遣人隨<ref type="person" target="#A000237">其</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0754a26"/>歸舍，具告所親，喻之出家。父母欣然，乃曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0754a27"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A003654">禪師</ref>佛法大龍，光被遠邇，緇門俊秀，歸者如<lb
ed="T" n="0754a28"/>雲。豈伊小騃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1308"/>，那堪擊訓，若垂虛受，<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>因</sic><corr>固</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz3"/>無留<lb
ed="T" n="0754a29"/>悋。」時年<date key="j19431271943492" from-iso="+0608-01-01" to-iso="+0608-12-31">七歲</date>也。至<placeName key="PL000000028114">雙峯</placeName>，習乎僧業，不逭艱<pb ed="T" n="0754b" xml:id="T50.2061.0754b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0754b01"/>辛。夜則歛容而坐，恬澹自居。洎受形俱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1189"/>，戒<lb
ed="T" n="0754b02"/>檢精厲。<persName key="A003654">信</persName>每以頓漸之旨，日省月試<ref type="person" target="#A000237">之</ref>。<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>聞<lb
ed="T" n="0754b03"/>言察理，觸事忘情，瘂正受塵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1309"/>，渴方飲水<lb
ed="T" n="0754b04"/>如也。<persName key="A003654">信</persName>知其可教，悉以其道授<ref type="person" target="#A000237">之</ref>。復命<lb
ed="T" n="0754b05"/>建浮圖，功畢，密付法衣以為質要。將知齕<lb
ed="T" n="0754b06"/>雪山之肥膩<ptr target="#n1304"/>，構作醍醐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g883"/>，飡海底之金剛，棲<lb
ed="T" n="0754b07"/>傾巨樹<ptr target="#n1305"/>。擁納之侶麕至<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1310"/>蟬聯<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1311"/>，商人不入於化<lb
ed="T" n="0754b08"/>城<ptr target="#n1306"/>，貧女大開於寶藏<ptr target="#n1307"/>，入其趣者號「東山法<lb
ed="T" n="0754b09"/>門」歟。以<date key="j19679201967920" when-iso="+0675-11-18">高宗上元二年十月二十三日</date>告<lb
ed="T" n="0754b10"/>滅<ptr target="#n1309"/>，報齡七十有四。是日氛霧冥暗，山石崩<lb
ed="T" n="0754b11"/>圯。門弟子<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>等奉瘞全身于<placeName key="PL000000028109">東山</placeName>之岡也。<lb
ed="T" n="0754b12"/>初，<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>於<date notBefore-iso="+0670-03-30" key="j19658611966270" notAfter-iso="+0671-05-13">咸<anchor xml:id="beg0754003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>享</sic><corr>亨</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0754003"/>初</date>命二、三禪子各言其志，<persName key="A009582">神<lb
ed="T" n="0754b13"/>秀</persName>先出偈，<persName key="A001719">惠能</persName>和焉。乃以法服付<persName key="A001719">慧能</persName>，受<lb
ed="T" n="0754b14"/>衣化於<placeName key="PL000000030617">韶陽</placeName>。<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>傳法<placeName key="PL000000027429">荊門</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛下</placeName>，南北之<lb
ed="T" n="0754b15"/>宗自茲始矣。又<persName key="A003654">信<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>甞於<placeName key="PL000000018846">九江</placeName>遙望<placeName key="PL000000028114">雙<lb
ed="T" n="0754b16"/>峯</placeName>，見紫雲如蓋，下有白氣，橫開六岐。<persName key="A003654">信</persName>謂<lb
ed="T" n="0754b17"/><persName key="A000237">忍</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A000237">汝</ref>知之乎？」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A003654">師</ref>之法旁出一<anchor xml:id="beg0754004"/>枝<anchor xml:id="end0754004"/>，相<lb
ed="T" n="0754b18"/>踵六世。」<persName key="A003654">信</persName>甚然之。及<persName key="A003867">法融</persName>化<placeName key="PL000000008579">金陵牛頭山</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0754b19"/>貽厥孫謀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g473"/>，至于<persName key="A010048">慧忠</persName>凡六人，號<persName key="G000021">牛頭六祖</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0754b20"/>此則<ref type="person" target="#A003654">四祖</ref>法又分枝矣。然<persName key="A003867">融</persName>望<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>則庶孽耳，<lb
ed="T" n="0754b21"/>安可匹嫡乎？<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13">開元中</date>，太子文學<persName key="A010052">閭丘均</persName>為塔<lb
ed="T" n="0754b22"/>碑焉。<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>勅諡<persName key="A000237">大滿禪師</persName>，塔曰<placeName key="PL000000056173">法雨</placeName>也。<placeName key="PL000000028083">蘄<lb
ed="T" n="0754b23"/>春</placeName>自<date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>季割屬偏覇<ptr target="#n1308"/>，暨<date from-iso="+0975-02-19" key="j20772212077574" to-iso="+0976-02-07">開寶乙亥歲</date>王師<lb
ed="T" n="0754b24"/>平<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>之前，<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>肉身墮淚如血珠焉。僧徒<lb
ed="T" n="0754b25"/>不測，乃李氏國亡之應也。今每歲孟冬，州人<lb
ed="T" n="0754b26"/>隣邑奔集作忌齋，猶成繁盛矣。其諱日將<lb
ed="T" n="0754b27"/>近，必雨霧陰<anchor xml:id="beg0754005"/>慘<anchor xml:id="end0754005"/>，不然霰雪交霏，至日則晴<lb
ed="T" n="0754b28"/>朗焉。</p>
